    dc:description "Figure 11. Notoprotella gordoni (Guiler, 1954) from off Botany Bay, New South Wales and eastern slope of Bass Strait, Tasmania. Male, 13.49 mm (estimated based on fig. 39 of Guerra-García and Takeuchi 2004), AM P.101912; female, 17.90 mm, AM E.6563. Bars indicate 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3673306/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

